<div class="container">
  <div class="real_cost_header">
    <h1>Real Cost of Coding Bootcamp</h1>
    <span><p>Based on your current salary and the cost of tuition from attending <%= @real_cost.bootcamp_id %>.</p><h3><strong><%= @real_cost.breakeven_time %> </strong>weeks to breakeven.</h3></span>
    <span><p>According to the national average salary, a Jr. Rails Developer makes $67,000 a year.</p><h3>This means a <strong><%= @real_cost.yearly_increase %>% </strong>increase in your yearly salary.</h3></span>
  </div>
</div>

<br>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-xs-4"> 
    <div class="text-center circle green">  
      <i class="fa fa-5x fa-usd"></i>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-center">$<%= @real_cost.true_cost %></h2>
    <h3 class="text-center green-text">REAL COST</h3>
    <p>Your true cost for attending this bootcamp</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-4 middle"> 
    <div class="text-center circle blue">  
      <i class="fa fa-5x fa-thumbs-down"></i>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-center">$<%= @real_cost.total_payment_due %></h2>
    <h3 class="text-center blue-text">TOTAL PAYMENT</h3>
    <p>Your total payment owed if you finance your bootcamp through Bootcamp Bucks</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-4 "> 
     <div class="text-center circle purple">  
      <i class="fa fa-5x fa-money"></i>
    </div>
     <h2 class="text-center">$<%= @real_cost.down_payment %></h2>
     <h3 class="text-center purple-text">DOWN PAYMENT</h3>
     <p>You will owe a down payment (25% of tuition)</p>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>
</p>$<%= @real_cost.down_payment %>



